{"tid":1567484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請各位兄弟姊妹手足幫幫手推list 左喺到嘅post，聽日915 極需要人，唔該幫幫手","createTime":"2019-09-14T05:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T02:58:26.000Z","uid":146535,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"0f7ea756a69da18fcf9a17ff3077b0494430773e","tid":1567484,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:46:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟姊妹手足，聽日我地915 港島見</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正視聽post 需要手足推同討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不再推未Fact Check 嘅內容<br />\n不指責，盡量做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同埋請大大力推915 嘅行動post，聽日係極需要各位嘅參與，請記住自己嘅憤怒，再用身體展示勇氣，對抗極權</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【力抗暴政 以善制惡】9.15 香港人行街攻略分析</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567381</a><br />\n<br />\n[美國政治第二課] 「香港人權及民主法案」有甚麼通關障礙？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eanBCS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eanBCS</a><br />\n<br />\n人手置頂 本周末（13-15/9）大型活動整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563302</a><br />\n<br />\n[國際民主日遊行攻略] 915 去港島遊行定入商場？溝埋做瀨尿牛丸咪得囉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563777\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563777</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我在新屋嶺的32小時</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRFczS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRFczS</a><br />\n<br />\n【司法覆核】女拔通識教師入稟申請推翻速龍小隊毋須展示警員編號<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eaboCS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eaboCS</a><br />\n<br />\n我哋唔要惠譽評級粒子彈？？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563251</a><br />\n<br />\n「免費」機票，黎緊一人同我出一張！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1562057\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1562057</a><br />\n<br />\n消防：傷者降級難過中六合彩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1562515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1562515</a><br />\n<br />\n消防記者會重點！處理果7個傷者都係清醒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563022</a><br />\n<br />\n林忌 : 連登大量流料假料洗腦，已經搞到周街信到十足，我地之前就笑藍絲被假料洗腦，家下自己呢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1562190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1562190</a><br />\n<br />\n我地無辦法阻止其他人食藍店，但我地可以推爆排爆所有黃店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1562746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1562746</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭開了第一槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1562178\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1562178</a>"},{"pid":"0f3abba1850907ed2e1aa4813b4c4f5a6f2b17c1","tid":1567484,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:47:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25a819790404988eb90a06ac1c03d8865e13369a","tid":1567484,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:50:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3c9100acc5254e76665a3f9c4f810214dbce3a6","tid":1567484,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:53:30.000Z","msg":"正視聽post 需要手足推同討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不再推未Fact Check 嘅內容<br />\n不指責，盡量做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>唔該大大力推915 嘅行動post，聽日係極需要各位嘅參與，請記住自己嘅憤怒，再用身體展示勇氣，對抗極權</strong><br />\n<br />\n請各位兄弟姊妹手足幫幫手推list 左喺到嘅post，聽日915 極需要人，唔該幫幫手<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567484</a>"},{"pid":"5085bdf28d061456e4b7c4169c9d8802d26d8fcb","tid":1567484,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:00:00.000Z","msg":"推"},